  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-brand mb-4">SEO Pricing in Swansea</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Good news: SEO in Swansea is more affordable than most Welsh business owners expect. Monthly retainers start from £497 for small businesses and go up to £1,997 for enterprise-level campaigns. Unlike agencies in Cardiff or Bristol that pad their fees with unnecessary overheads, working with a Swansea-based team means you get strong ROI at a sensible price. Local keyword competition is lower, and because we are right here in Swansea, we can be more responsive and hands-on with the businesses we serve.</p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">This page lays out exactly what you get at each price point, what one-off services cost, and how to figure out whether SEO is a worthwhile investment for your particular business. No vague quotes, no hidden fees, no nasty surprises on the invoice.</p>

    <div class="bg-teal-50 border-l-4 border-teal-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg my-6">
      <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Quick Answer</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">SEO in Swansea costs between £497 and £1,997 per month depending on how many keywords you are targeting, what content you need, and how competitive your market is. One-off audits start from £297. Every plan is rolling monthly with no lock-in. Most businesses see measurable improvements within 3-4 months.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Why Transparent Pricing Matters</h2>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Let's be honest: the SEO industry has a reputation problem. Too many agencies hide behind "bespoke quotes" and "it depends" because they want to charge whatever each client will stomach. That works for the agency, not for the business owner.</p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Transparent pricing does three things. First, you can budget properly before we even have a conversation. Second, it forces us to spell out exactly what you get for your money. Third, it builds trust because there is nothing tucked away in the small print. A restaurant on <strong>Mumbles seafront</strong> and a tradesman working out of <strong>Morriston</strong> have very different budgets and very different needs. Clear tiers let each choose the right level of investment without any pressure.</p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">We publish our prices because we are confident in what they deliver. Every line item listed below is something we actually do each month, not padding to justify the fee. If you want to compare us with other providers, you will find our <a href="/services/" class="text-brand hover:underline">full service descriptions</a> just as straightforward.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Monthly SEO Plans</h2>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Every plan runs on a rolling monthly basis. No minimum terms, no exit penalties. You stay because the results make it worth staying.</p>

