    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Not sure which plan is right for you? <a href="/free-seo-audit-swansea/" class="text-brand hover:underline">Grab a free SEO audit</a> and we will recommend the right tier based on where you stand, who you are up against, and what you want to achieve.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">One-Off SEO Services</h2>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Not every business needs a monthly retainer. These standalone services give you expert insight without an ongoing commitment. Each one comes with a detailed report and prioritised actions you can implement yourself or pass to your developer.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-8">
      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">SEO Audit</h3>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand">£297</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">Full review of your on-page SEO, keyword positioning, content gaps, and quick-win opportunities. Delivered as a prioritised action plan.</p>
        <a href="/seo-audit-swansea/" class="text-brand hover:underline text-sm font-medium">Learn more</a>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Technical Audit</h3>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand">£497</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">Deep crawl analysis covering site speed, indexation, Core Web Vitals, structured data, mobile usability, and crawl budget efficiency.</p>
        <a href="/technical-seo-swansea/" class="text-brand hover:underline text-sm font-medium">Learn more</a>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">AI Search Readiness Audit</h3>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand">£397</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">Assessment of how your site performs in AI-powered search engines like Google AI Overviews, ChatGPT, and Perplexity. Includes citation optimisation strategy.</p>
        <a href="/ai-search-optimisation-swansea/" class="text-brand hover:underline text-sm font-medium">Learn more</a>
